{"tid":2248443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國學生領袖投案准保釋　曾高唱《榮光》給港人打氣","createTime":"2020-10-18T14:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T09:13:27.000Z","uid":70964,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"364b28e6be2a552f90bfe7a700d30f5ef8806699","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgPcYgkj9II\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLgPcYgkj9II&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=1928c765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgPcYgkj9II</a>"},{"pid":"4081a6b3c5b61fc4c2f420b85fbc525c17dc2f08","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"泰國學生領袖Francis J. Bunkueanun Paothong被警方通緝，指他涉嫌阻礙皇家車隊...意圖攻擊、傷害泰國王后素堤達的人身安全與自由。他主動到警署投案。<br />\n<br />\n泰國人權律師團表示，社運人士艾格猜(Ekachai Hongkangwan)以及學生領袖Francis J. Bunkueanun Paothong周五已被泰國警方以泰國刑法第110條起訴。<br />\n<br />\n有律師解釋，泰國刑法第110條規定，任何人侵害國王、王后、皇室後裔以及攝者的人身安全及自由，都可被判16年至20年的監禁，如果情節嚴重，更可以判終身監禁、甚至死刑。<br />\n<br />\nFrancis周六傍晚6時許在Twitter表示已獲准保釋，須繳交20萬泰銖保釋金，即約5萬港元，又指在案件審結前，無法就案件發表任何評論。他亦向所有支持他的人士表達謝意。<br />\n<br />\nFrancis進入警署前，他說了一番話，最後忍不住哭了：「終有一天，我能重拾我的自由，我能平反我是清白。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「我現在身處警署前面，我被控兩日前意圖傷害王后，警方已經發出逮捕令，現在我站在這裡，希望主動證明我是清白，我希望能以真相說服人：我並沒有打算傷害王后或王室任何人。」<br />\n「在這個關鍵時刻，我將會失去我的自由、失去我的自由意志。在這個案件，我甚或會失去我人生所有、我的家人、我的朋友&hellip;&hellip;當下而言，我並不確定能否成功證明自己的清白。但我必須相信，保持希望才能繼續前行。所以，只要我還能呼吸，我會一直保持著希望&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n說到這裡，他不禁拭淚。他說：「終有一天，我能重拾我的自由，我能平反我是清白&hellip;&hellip;我一直追求目標仍在等我。在面對我的命運之前，我想跟大家分享我最尊敬的美國故總統羅斯福的說話：The only limit to our realization of tomorrow will be our doubts of today. Let us move forward with strong and active faith.（今日的疑慮，會是實現明天的唯一障礙，讓我們抱著強大的信念前行。）」<br />\n<br />\n最後，他說：「不用擔心我，我會為泰國人民、為奶茶聯盟、為你而戰。」<br />\n<br />\n10月1日，他在中國駐曼谷大使館附近高唱《願榮光歸香港》，給香港人打氣。"},{"pid":"50c60131d4a8e9d2a794d36b2a56672cb930b93f","tid":2248443,"uid":30503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"泰國人加油"},{"pid":"f31b8a099d3dc1a94691be19e9121ed2b633e938","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"泰國人加油"},{"pid":"81aec610925ed5c2ae953aba2cf466ae7f7a289a","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"III"},{"pid":"b6ba79517fb5387fdd9f80f6e50118b98d5e7c53","tid":2248443,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"泰國人死刑都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa8361516a93629576beac917e7a1d42eeef81d","tid":2248443,"uid":84465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"Francis is cute"},{"pid":"cb3fcaa545c6afdd722981c77dff9b6007500518","tid":2248443,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"泰國人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d20eace782244fab9c404c79cf46633067db4d","tid":2248443,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"支持泰國手足"},{"pid":"f27b2c40aa9e19247c49ffe9ed8b3379f0586fe1","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"支持泰國手足"},{"pid":"1f4e12afcab7784ae9b283f29beb736558187aa1","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVkLkn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVkLkn4.jpg&h=56ecca06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4721edc03e617d1213e2fce2640f050d7dccb81","tid":2248443,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ba79517fb5387fdd9f80f6e5011